Note: can also create a .gvimrc for gvim config settings; symlink similarly

Installation: Create symlinks:
    
    ln -s ~/config/.vim ~/.vim
    ln -s ~/config/.vimrc ~/.vimrc

Adding non-plugin stuff: (in .vim directory)

    git add <directory or file path>
    git commit -m "description"
    git push

Getting latest version: (in .vim directory)

    git pull
